LinkableBase * m_anchor

Detailed Description

A linked list chains a variable number of objects, which provide the two methods Type* GetNext() and SetNext(Type *next).

LinkableBase * LinkedListBase::GetBack (   )  const
 

Returns a pointer to the last element of the linked list. Please note that GetBack has to iterate all elements of the linked list and thus will show bad performance in long lists.
